'''怪蟹科'''（學名：{{lang|la|Geryonidae}}）是[[梭子蟹總科|梭子蟹總科]]之下七個[[科_(生物)|科]]之一，其物種均為深海性物種，棲息於深海<ref name="manning1989two"/>。

==形態特徵==
本科物種的[[背甲|背甲]]呈六角形，前緣側面有三至五顆鋸齒狀的[[齒突|齒突]]。腹部有七節體節。形態與[[梭子蟹科|梭子蟹科]]類似，{{tsl|ja|鉗脚|鉗足}}比[[步足|步足]]短，第五對腳扁平作鰭狀<ref name="karasawa2008revision">{{cite journal|title=Revision of Portunoidea Rafinesque, 1815 (Decapoda: Brachyura) with emphasis on the fossil genera and families|author=Karasawa, Hiroaki and Schweitzer, Carrie E and Feldmann, Rodney M|journal=Journal of Crustacean Biology|volume=28|issue=1|pages=82-127|year=2008}}</ref><ref name="manning1989two">{{cite journal|title=Two new genera and nine new species of geryonid crabs (Crustacea, Decapoda, Geryonidae)|author=Manning, Raymond B and Holthuis, LB|journal=Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington|volume=102|number=1|pages=50-77|year=1989}}</ref>。

